    <div class="about-text">
      <h2>Passionate about design that <span>solves real problems.</span></h2>
      <p>I'm Chandradevi S, a UI/UX designer and B.Sc IT student at Bharathiar University (2nd year, graduating 2027). I'm from Tamil Nadu, India, and I design digital experiences that are clean, intuitive, and built to work for real people.</p>
      <p>My work spans mobile app design (FABLO — 13 screens end-to-end), web portfolios for creative professionals, and poster/banner design for events. I use Figma as my primary tool, and I'm also comfortable with Adobe XD and Canva.</p>
      <p>I'm currently open to <strong style="color:var(--purple);">freelance UI/UX projects</strong>, remote collaborations, and internship opportunities globally. I work well with international clients and communicate clearly in English.</p>
